{
  "text": "BCS was assessed using a 5-point scale [CITATION_1] . 1: emaciated, 2: lean, 3: ideal, 4: overweight, 5: obese. The dogs were weighed on a set of scales (Marsden Group). All body condition scoring and weighing of the dogs was completed in 2014 by GN and in 2015 by CB, who were trained by PY who has extensive experience in this procedure. The interviewer's assessment of BCS and BW of each dog was taken as the gold standard.",
